Text:
Sup all... Happy Birthday to Lil Wayne... We will blaze a dube in your honour bro, 
And now I Am Not a Human Being is the upcoming eighth studio album by American rapper 
Lil Wayne. The album will be released digitally on September 27, 2010, coinciding with 
Wayne's birthday. The physical version of the album will be released on October 12, 2010. 
This is the fifth album of Lil Wayne recording outside Tha Carter series of albums...
